snippet.title: Athenian Rhapsody MOTHER DIRECT 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
The best way to support Athenian Rhapsody is to Wishlist the game on Steam and follow the socials - Give the demo Thunder Goober's Personality Dungeon a play to earn Tokens, which you can reward for items in the full game! Release details are in the video.

Socials and Steam Page:
https://linktr.ee/athenianrhapsody

Link to Mother Direct's Steam Event: https://nokogodo.com/motherlike

Link to Mother Direct's CHARITY MERCH: https://jobjobllc.com/collections/mother-direct-23

Athenian Rhapsody's Music by Arpbug, the game's composer:
https://soundcloud.com/arpbug
